-- Wachovia shares drop further on Citi deal
-- 
-- Mon Sep 29, 2008 8:44am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/29/us-markets-stocks-wachovia-idUSTRE48S3D120080929

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Wachovia Corp extended losses and were down 80.9 percent at $1.91 before the opening bell on Monday after the Federal Deposit Insurance Corp said Citigroup will buy the bank's operations. 

 Citigroup's shares rose 3.2 percent to $20.80. (Editing by Kenneth Barry)